<TEXT>
<P>
I watch old reruns of "I Love Lucy," "Sanford and Son" and "The Honeymooners" 
and they still make me laugh. The other night I watched "Roseanne" for the 
first time and I didn't laugh once during the whole show. Have I lost my sense 
of humor? Should I go see a psychiatrist? 
</P>
<P>
Frederick D. Mullen, Upland 
</P>
