<TEXT>
<P>
QUOTE OF THE WEEK: We've seen some pretty odd couples -- but rap icons Ice T, 
Slick Rick and Fab Five Freddy with . . . Malcolm Forbes? It all happened at 
MTV's noisy post-Grammy's Rap Party, where the world's hippest 69-year-old 
Capitalist Kingpin (and frequent Liz Taylor date) mixed with rap royalty like 
