<P>
Photo, Dave Huskins, left, and Terry Cover cast aluminum at the Laurel Aluminum 
Casting Co., which is housed in the old Copperweld Corp. plant in Glassport, 
Pa., near Pittsburgh. Associated Press 
</P>
