<TYPE>
<P>
Letter to the Editor 
</P>
</TYPE>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA030589-0093 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 26644 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
March 5, 1989, Sunday, Home Edition 
