Israeli soldiers blocked roads and turned back hundreds of Israeli peace 
activists hoping to meet and discuss peace with Palestinians in the occupied 
West Bank. But several hundred others sneaked through or were allowed to pass, 
organizers said. About 1,500 supporters of the Peace Now movement set out from 
