Lee &amp; Sakahara of Costa Mesa is the architect and the Peridian Group of 
Irvine, the landscape architect. John A. Alexander Co. of Santa Fe Springs and 
Prizio &amp; Prizio of Fountain Valley are general contractors. Nippon Credit 
Bank Ltd. of Japan will provide construction financing. Cushman &amp; Wakefield 
are the leasing agents. 
