<P>
Game Story; Full Run 
</P>
</TYPE>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA030589-0269 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 27294 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
March 5, 1989, Sunday, Orange County Edition 
</P>
