<HEADLINE>
<P>
AIRLINE TOLL-FREE NUMBERS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Aeroflot (212) 397-1660 
</P>
<P>
Aer Lingus (800) 223-6537 
</P>
<P>
Aerolineas Argentinas (800) 333-0276 
